WaitFor (script event)
======================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game\_class) type [idThread](Thread\_(scripting)), accessible via [sys](Scripting\_basics#sys) identifier.

Description
-----------

Waits for entity to complete it's move.

Usage
-----

*[void](Data\_types#void)* waitFor( *[entity](Data\_types#entity)* **mover** )

Parameters
----------

[mover] - entity to wait for.

Parameter only supports entities of following [spawn classes](Spawn\_class):

![](/images/images_2_23_D3square_25.png) Doom 3: idCameraAnim, idMover, idMover\_Binary.

![](/images/images_e_e8_Q4square_25.png) Quake 4: idCameraAnim, idMover, idMover\_Binary, rvSplineMover

